100% Polyester

name: Stick It To 'Em Logo Sport Duffel Bag - Grey
description:
This roomy duffel is just right for workouts or overnight trips. Stick It To 'Em logo embroidered sets your bag apart from the rest. Monument Grey/Black color.

*600 denier polyester with 1680 denier ballistic polyester accents
*Durable, water-resistant PVC bottom
*D-shape opening with two-way zipper for easy packing
*Detachable, adjustable padded shoulder strap
*Padded carrying handle
*Sturdy web handles
*Shoe/wet pocket with mesh inserts for ventilation
*Dimensions: 12"h x 19"w x 12"d; approx. 2,736 cubic inches
